trans-unit.source: Represents a group of annotations.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en gruppe med kommentarer.

trans-unit.source: The AnnotationGroup class represents a collection of annotations.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AnnotationGroup representerer en samling av kommentarer.

trans-unit.source: This class can be used to manipulate annotations relative to each other.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan brukes til å endre kommentarer i forhold til hverandre.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the content alignment of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir justeringen innhold for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: This property is used to align text for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TextAnnotation>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.CalloutAnnotation> objects, and to align a nonscaled image inside an <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ImageAnnotation> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes til å justere tekst for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TextAnnotation>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.CalloutAnnotation>objekter, og til å justere nonscaled bildet i et <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ImageAnnotation>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ImageAnnotation> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.CalloutAnnotation> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TextAnnotation>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.ContentAlignment"></xref> value that represents the content alignment of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.ContentAlignment"> </xref> verdi som representerer innhold justeringen for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations in the group.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av merknader i gruppen.

trans-unit.source: Note that the coordinates of all annotations in the group are relative to the group annotation.
trans-unit.target: Merk at koordinatene til alle merknader i gruppen i forhold til gruppen merknaden.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Henter merknadstypen.

trans-unit.source: This property is used to get the name of each annotation type, for example.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes til å hente navnet på hver merknadstypen, for eksempel.

trans-unit.source: Line, Rectangle, Ellipse, and so forth.
trans-unit.target: Linje rektanglet, ellipsen og så videre.

trans-unit.source: The annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Merknadstypen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background color of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used for the background of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukt for bakgrunn for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background gradient style of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsstilen gradering for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Two colors are used to draw the gradient, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackSecondaryColor%2A>.
trans-unit.target: To farger brukes til å tegne til gradering, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackSecondaryColor%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackSecondaryColor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.GradientStyle"></xref> value used to draw the background of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.GradientStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunn for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the hatch style of an annotation background.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir skraveringsstilen for merknadsbakgrunnen.

trans-unit.source: Two colors are used to draw the hatching, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackSecondaryColor%2A>.
trans-unit.target: To farger brukes til å tegne skravering, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackSecondaryColor%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackSecondaryColor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartHatchStyle"></xref> value used to draw the background of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartHatchStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunn for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the secondary color for the background of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den sekundære fargen for bakgrunn for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: A secondary color is used with <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A> when <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackHatchStyle%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackGradientStyle%2A> are used.
trans-unit.target: En sekundær farge brukes med <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A>når <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackHatchStyle%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackGradientStyle%2A>brukes.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackGradientStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackHatchStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationGroup.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the background with hatching or gradient fill.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunnen skravering eller gradering fyll.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the chart area to which the annotation is clipped.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på diagramområdet merknaden er beskåret.

trans-unit.source: If a chart area name is specified, the annotation will only be drawn inside the plotting area of that chart area.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en navnet på diagramområdet som er angitt, blir bare merknaden tegnes i tegneområdet for dette diagramområdet.

trans-unit.source: All parts of the annotation outside of the plotting area will be clipped.
trans-unit.target: Alle deler av merknaden utenfor tegneområdet beskjæres.

trans-unit.source: To disable chart area clipping, set this property to <xref:System.Double.NaN> or an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil deaktivere beskjæring området, kan du angi denne egenskapen <xref:System.Double.NaN>eller en tom streng.</xref:System.Double.NaN>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> that represents the name of an existing chart area.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> som representerer navnet på et eksisterende diagramområdet.

trans-unit.source: Releases unmanaged and, optionally, managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Versjoner uforvaltet, og eventuelt administreres ressurser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> to release both unmanaged and managed resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både uforvaltede og behandlede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the font to use for the text of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir skriften som skal brukes for teksten for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Font"></xref> object used for the text of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Font"> </xref> objekt som brukes for teksten for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text color for an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tekstfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used for the text color of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukt for tekstfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that determines if an annotation is selected.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som bestemmer om en merknad er valgt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the annotation is selected, otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis en merknad er valgt, ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that specifies whether the size of an annotation is always defined in relative chart coordinates.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som angir om størrelsen på en merknad alltid defineres med relative diagramkoordinater.

trans-unit.source: The height and width of an annotation may be set in relative chart or in axes coordinates.
trans-unit.target: Høyden og bredden på en merknad kan angis i relativ diagrammet eller akser koordinater.

trans-unit.source: By default, relative chart coordinates are used.
trans-unit.target: Som standard brukes relative diagramkoordinater.

trans-unit.source: To use axes coordinates, set the IsSizeAlwaysRelative property to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil bruke akser koordinatene egenskapen IsSizeAlwaysRelative til `false`.

trans-unit.source: Then either anchor the annotation to a data point or set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.AxisX%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.AxisY%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Deretter enten forankrer merknaden ett datapunkt eller sett den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.AxisX%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.AxisY%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.AxisY%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.AxisX%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.Width*> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.Height*> of an annotation are always in chart relative coordinates, otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis den <> </> *> og <> </> *> for en merknad er alltid med relative diagramkoordinater, ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line color of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjefargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw an annotation line.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne et merknadslinjen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line style of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjestilen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"></xref> value used to draw an annotation line.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne et merknadslinjen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line width, in pixels, of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjetykkelse, i piksler for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: An <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> value defining the width, in pixels, of an annotation line.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""> </xref> verdi definerer bredden på en merknadslinjen i piksler.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the color of the annotation's shadow.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir fargen på skyggen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the shadow of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne skyggen for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the size of the annotation's shadow.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir størrelsen på skyggen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: An <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> value that represents the offset between an annotation and its shadow.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""> </xref> verdi som Representer forskyvningen mellom en merknad og skyggen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text style of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tekststilen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A TextStyle value used to draw the text of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: En tekststilen-verdi som brukes til å tegne teksten for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that indicates whether the annotation is visible.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som indikerer om en merknad er synlig.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the annotation is visible, otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis en merknad er synlig, ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
